Class SQLDataDao

  • java.lang.Object
    • by.horant.fintask.dao.impl.SQLDataDao
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataDAO

    public class SQLDataDao
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataDAO
    This class is an implementation of the DataDAO interface and thus provides interaction with the database for obtaining various list of entity objects, implementing such methods as obtaining users, receiving orders, obtaining drugs and obtaining the requested recipes.
    Author:
    Anton Horbach
